{"tid":2420720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.28暴動手足無錢開飯都唔搵基金幫手,咁大件事無人講?","createTime":"2021-02-24T05:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T16:22:14.000Z","uid":100291,"like":68,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"29f2872245263c6fa7f444911175597717ecd3ad","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>728手足<span class=\"red\">正式開審</span>,坐足60日</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o09OoZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo09OoZn.png&h=3bd2ad16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/ZCDZFLO7UFGGXF5MVBNU3OPNJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FZCDZFLO7UFGGXF5MVBNU3OPNJU%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=87fc6727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FZCDZFLO7UFGGXF5MVBNU3OPNJU%2F&h=546da736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/ZCDZFLO7UFGGXF5MVBNU3OPNJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>審訊期內番唔到工,連飯都就黎無得食</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>如果想支持佢地不如直接課金比佢地啦</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLFt8so.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLFt8so.png&h=6236f295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不好意思，這個人血饅頭可以吃一口嗎？<br />\n關於開設這個Patreon 的原因<br />\n<br />\n老實就是為了錢啊，不然呢？<br />\n<br />\n我知道或許有人又會指控食人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n對啊 我正吃自己的人血<br />\n<br />\n作為一個freelance 本來就不多積蓄（對不起我廢）<br />\n<br />\n被捕後初期情緒有影響疫情有影響工作收入不穩定<br />\n<br />\n加上家裡在上庭前數月發生了重大的影響<br />\n<br />\n使不得不擔上更多責任<br />\n<br />\n審訊期內無法上班確實是一個難題<br />\n<br />\n無可奈何下，想到開設這個Patreon<br />\n<br />\n也會好奇，到底<span class=\"red\"><strong>沒有巨乳無碼大奶奶照片</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n會不會有人願意付款進來看看這個厭世傷春悲秋的Patreon（當然我會儘可能的post上很多可愛的貓狗照讓各位貴賓好好吸貓吸狗一下）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/bu-hao-yi-si-zhe-47910639?utm_medium=clipboard_copy&amp;utm_source=copy_to_clipboard&amp;utm_campaign=postshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2Fbu-hao-yi-si-zhe-47910639%3Futm_medium%3Dclipboard_copy%26utm_source%3Dcopy_to_clipboard%26utm_campaign%3Dpostshare&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=f785c04f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/bu-hao-yi-si-zhe-47910639?utm_medium=clipboard_copy&amp;utm_source=copy_to_clipboard&amp;utm_campaign=postshare</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>好撚慘</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/days-1-ping-fu-47894220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2Fdays-1-ping-fu-47894220&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=9216fc40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/days-1-ping-fu-47894220</a><br />\n<br />\n上庭前「赴湯杜火」夫婦給了我們每人一個平安符。<br />\n<br />\n符是魂，代表靈界的公文，咒則是魄，表示靈界的密碼，再配合一些手印及步罡，就能獲得神明的助力，以達趨吉避凶並消災解厄。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這個平安符將陪伴著我們，渡過六十天。</strong>"},{"pid":"dbbae6de8e2ef0f57107c6b108f24fdda7335ac9","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29192963a22b523596c69f36a5e5a56b8f3197","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21482ef86ef123b50388d7b3f634cf1ee23839d6","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9857ee9931231139c54d948c22d65c1cbef57e32","tid":2420720,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42b4b86b4e048704a473cdce4472d916bcb83de","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b0d90cad3db61b41bc356ace0d2d6df8245780","tid":2420720,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39ed057fd94271d0f260e6c7965743ad8f77dd4","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85afd93cae1005c508ae3c68b575ba08be0773e","tid":2420720,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足無人理"},{"pid":"b03fe6f1ca1d7a4524a9c6faa7dc70c6c1eb484d","tid":2420720,"uid":1